MANY people around the world want to own their dream cars, but how does it really cost to maintain super and hyper cars? In a video of published by Houston Crosta on YouTube, Royal Exotic Cars dealership shows how many hours and what it costs to do an oil change in a Bugatti Veyron. The mechanic needs to remove the oil, which looks like the easy part. However, removing the covers underneath the car reveals the much more complicated process that leads to 16 drain plugs.  